b'My title at @MasterClass is going to be VP of Creative Innovation. Together with a bunch of my teammates from HITRECORD, we\xe2\x80\x99re going to work on coming up with new and cool ways for people to find their creative selves and grow as artists.\n\n(3/5)'

b'The HITRECORD community is going to remain independent.

(2/5)'

b'HITRECORD has landed an exit!
